{"tid":1963624,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"20到中，有冇人開始覺得生活好膚燥","createTime":"2020-04-08T09:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T00:20:58.000Z","uid":244066,"like":19,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"74a4c164aa18174f6efcd63d825abb89ae2775f0","tid":1963624,"uid":244066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />估唔到咁快有中年危機<br />\n本身份工好穩定，人工唔錯儲緊錢準備3年內買樓<br />\n但就係因為咁，好似已經冇咩野要去鬥，過下日晨就得<br />\n<br />\n以前都會打下機，但人大左唔知係D遊戲冇咁吸引，定係已經真係唔係好鍾意玩<br />\n居然可以日日睇下YOUTUBE...HEA下就一日<br />\n成人同自己講搵野學下，學下語文好..健身好...咩都好<br />\n但就冇動力，硬係覺得學左練左好似都冇咩分別<br />\n所以為左增值下報左MASTER黎讀，但又好似讀完2年之後又會變返依家咁<br />\n<br />\n而且發現除左買樓..建立家庭外，真係冇咩想追求<br />\nd人會買下衫...食下好西...玩下d高價少少既興趣例如音響攝影<br />\n我通通都冇興趣，好處係真係洗好少錢<br />\n但有時又真係諗，咁樣既生活有咩意義?<br />\n<br />\n明明20到中應該係人生先岩岩開始<br />\n好似好多人生活都好多姿多采，但我就已經成個廢老咁<br />\n人生唔係冇目標，但唔係依刻可以實現到<br />\n<br />\n到底係幸福既事，定係好慘<br />\n以前都唔會成日諗以前，但依家成日好想返返去以前<br />\n享受下中學時光...享受下一齊落街玩下gameboy既日子<br />\n依家已經冇得再黎..."},{"pid":"98ffcbaaa02bd317ecd427e2dbfc521125febca8","tid":1963624,"uid":55189,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"慘過你 連買樓.建立家庭都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca61c06f97390bf652696b32c9eb59ee2a44fa13","tid":1963624,"uid":23271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:12:30.000Z","msg":"學下盈盈樂樂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866ba4bf20d82457b09230337e422fbdfb9dff7e","tid":1963624,"uid":333199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:13:37.000Z","msg":"返工為生存<br />\n<br />\n儲錢啦<br />\n<br />\n為左自己有錢續命到去65歲退休，等政府養"},{"pid":"06d0d11518521765e5d5ad154ebe2da1be9987c5","tid":1963624,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"巴打做到咩位 可以去買樓<br />\n係咪Big 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b318f71c804260b9d0700f68647a887e7231164","tid":1963624,"uid":262914,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"我人生唯一娛樂就係去旅行"},{"pid":"168bd7b58b5118dde4accac8f6ac6997766abf51","tid":1963624,"uid":99421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"懷念大學既日子 無憂無慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93db07880a4877f8c0664b6fcfecc55c2ea1d72","tid":1963624,"uid":244066,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"98ffcbaaa02bd317ecd427e2dbfc521125febca8","tid":1963624,"uid":55189,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:12:21.000Z","msg":"慘過你 連買樓.建立家庭都唔想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:15:55.000Z","msg":"每個人追求既野都唔同既<br />\n我有時都會都諗，20到中唔應該係咁<br />\n所以都會諗下其他人追求緊D咩<br />\n硬係覺得佢地好多野做，生活好豐富<br />\n我就過得一日得一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生活上好多野都滿意，屋企人好，愛情冇咩問題，工作好<br />\n但矛盾既係，又好似好多野都唔滿意<br />\n20到中既心態明明唔應該咁廢，明明唔應該咁無所事事"},{"pid":"ac25b77e12773a7cc0cdc2ea523964d79ca3e974","tid":1963624,"uid":244066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06d0d11518521765e5d5ad154ebe2da1be9987c5","tid":1963624,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"巴打做到咩位 可以去買樓<br />\n係咪Big 4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:17:24.000Z","msg":"學位職系"},{"pid":"9c5b8d4c67096c5d127a543dd9a7a90064b8b963","tid":1963624,"uid":244066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"168bd7b58b5118dde4accac8f6ac6997766abf51","tid":1963624,"uid":99421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"懷念大學既日子 無憂無慮<img src=\"/assets/face